self.title: CDISC SEND Pregnancy Outcome Response Terminology

definition: Terminology relevant for pregnancy outcome responses.
name: Pregnancy Outcome Response
preferredTerm: CDISC SEND Pregnancy Outcome Response Terminology

terms.definition: Loss of all or part of the products of conception prior to the scheduled c-section date or expected delivery date.
A birth event that occurs prior to the scheduled c-section date or expected delivery date.
A pregnancy result for a female that had one to many live births.
A pregnancy result for a female that had all intrauterine deaths.
